data.description: This home has so much potential, and with the right vision, could be your new paradise. 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in the Cypress Lakes subdivision, guarantees privacy and convenience to NSB Kingsbay and downtown St Marys. Spacious living and dining area right off the galley kitchen. The kitchen features updated laminate counter tops, about a dozen cabinets, and a large window for natural light. Sitting on an acre of land, with plenty of space to roam, this home includes a screened-in porch to enjoy all seasons! Indoor laundry room, outside storage shed, easy to maintain vinyl siding, and neutral colors. With this price tag, it's sure to go quick, so call faster to see!
